name: Universe #120
description: Universe #120 - Revroe was a beauty to behold with it's amazing horizons. 120 was hesistant to approact the universe for aeons. It made it's way slowly towards it for centuries but Revroe was aware. It put defenses against it but at it's core, it succumbed to the love 120 held for it. Their bonding was slow but strong. Now they are together forever.
